rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Okay, the ferry from here
goes directly to Aletta.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Okay,
but why a passenger ferry?

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Since His Majesty the Emperor
is coming with us, shouldn't we just
take his fancy ship?

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Even though I am accompanying Adel,
my actions are unofficial.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0006
rows.name:
His Majesty's flagship
is also a warship.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0007
rows.name:
Entering Iiran territory
would require complex
negotiations beforehand.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0009
rows.name:
You have a look on your face like
you're about to say we should
just force our way through.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0011
rows.name:
To think the one who wields the
immense power of the Heaven's Holy
Grail could be so simple-minded.

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0012
rows.name: Hey, I haven't said a word yet!

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0013
rows.name:
Come on, isn't a relaxing trip
better than being on
the stuffy flagship anyway?

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0014
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] The resistance army,
a gathering of people who adore Adel...
I'm kind of looking forward to it...

rows.label: fev11_340_150_msg0015
rows.name:
Now that we're all on the same page,
shall we go talk to the captain
and get going?
